page_title: Understanding Azure OpenAI Service deployment types
page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI deployment types | Global-Standard | Standard | Provisioned.
chunk_content: StandardStandard deployments provide a pay-per-call billing model on the chosen model. Provides the fastest way to get started as you only pay for what you consume. Models available in each region as well as throughput may be limited.  Standard deployments are optimized for low to medium volume workloads with high burstiness. Customers with high consistent volume may experience greater latency variability.
